results.name: a(n) = Product_{h == 5 (mod 6) and h|n} h.
comment: Not multiplicative: a(5)*a(7) <> a(35). - _R. J. Mathar_, Oct 08 2011
maple: A140214 := proc(n) a := 1 ; for h in numtheory[divisors](n) do if (h mod 6) = 5 then a := a*h: fi; od: a; end:
results.author: _R. J. Mathar_, Jun 27 2008
